document.title: Contact
document.description: Contact us for any questions or concerns about West Maid.

body.raw:
If you have any questions or concerns about West Maid, please contact us using one of the methods below. We will try to respond as soon as possible.

## Contact Information

-   **Email:** [contact@westmaid.com.au](mailto:contact@westmaid.com.au)

document.description: The Privacy Policy for West Maid.

body.raw:
Your privacy is very important to us. Accordingly, we have developed this Policy in order for you to understand how we collect, use, communicate, and disclose and make use of personal information. The following outlines our privacy policy.

1. **Purpose Identification:** Before or at the time of collecting personal information, we will identify the purposes for which information is being collected.

2. **Objective Collection and Use:** We will collect and use personal information solely with the objective of fulfilling those purposes specified by us and for other compatible purposes, unless we obtain the consent of the individual concerned or as required by law.

3. **Retention Period:** We will only retain personal information as long as necessary for the fulfillment of those purposes.

4. **Lawful and Fair Collection:** We will collect personal information by lawful and fair means and, where appropriate, with the knowledge or consent of the individual concerned.

5. **Relevance and Accuracy:** Personal data should be relevant to the purposes for which it is to be used, and, to the extent necessary for those purposes, should be accurate, complete, and up-to-date.

6. **Security Safeguards:** We will protect personal information by reasonable security safeguards against loss or theft, as well as unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, use, or modification.

7. **Information Accessibility:** We will make readily available to customers information about our policies and practices relating to the management of personal information.

We are committed to conducting our business in accordance with these principles to ensure that the confidentiality of personal information is protected and maintained.

West Maid Pty Ltd (West Maid) operates an online platform at [www.westmaid.com.au](https://www.westmaid.com.au) (the Website) through which customers (Users) can book a cleaner for the provision of cleaning services (Cleaning Services), by submitting a Booking Request. West Maid then matches the most suitable cleaner from its database of cleaners to the booking request.

This is a contract between West Maid and the users.

The cleaner is in the business of providing cleaning services.

West Maid enters into agreements with Users for and on behalf of cleaners for the provision of cleaning Services to users.

The user enters into two contractual relationships. The first contract being with West Maid, governing the access to and use of the website accordance with the terms and conditions of this agreement. The second contract being with West Maid as agent for the cleaner for the provision of the cleaning services (Cleaning Agreement).

The User is deemed to have entered into this Contract and a contractual relationship with West Maid through the making and acceptance of a Booking.

## AND THE PARTIES HEREBY AGREE:

Access to and use of the website is subject to the terms and conditions outlined in this agreement (the Terms).

### 1. DEFINITIONS AND INTERPRETATION

#### 1.1. In these Terms (including the recitals), unless the context otherwise requires:

-   **Booking:** means the booking made by you on the Website for the provision of Cleaning Services;

-   **Booking System:** means the online system which enables you to make a Booking;

-   **Cleaning Fee:** means the fee, as advised by West Maid from time to time, (inclusive of goods and service tax, if applicable) for the Cleaning Services charged on an hourly basis or flat price and invoiced by West Maid;

-   **Intellectual Property Rights:** means all present and future rights anywhere in the world in relation to copyright, trademarks, designs, patents, or other proprietary rights, or any rights to registration of such rights whether existing before or after your access to the Website;

-   **Payment Amount:** means the amount that you are required to pay for the Cleaning Services under your Booking;

-   **Site Content:** means all material, content, and information made available on the Website including but not limited to written text, graphics, images, photographs, logos, trademarks, audio material, video material, and any other forms of expression;

-   **you, your:** means you as the user of the Website.

#### 1.2. In these Terms, unless the context otherwise requires:

(a) headings are for convenience only and do not affect its interpretation or construction;

(b) the singular includes the plural and vice versa;

(c) references to recitals, clauses, subclauses, paragraphs, annexures or schedules are references to recitals, clauses, subclauses, paragraphs, annexures, and schedules of or to these Terms;

(d) words importing a gender include other genders;

(e) the word person means a natural person and any association, body or entity whether incorporated or not;

(f) where any word or phrase is defined, any other part of speech or other grammatical forms of that word or phrase has a cognate meaning;

(g) a reference to any statute, proclamation, rule, code, regulation or ordinance includes any amendment, consolidation, modification, re-enactment or reprint of it or any statute, proclamation, rule, code, regulation or ordinance replacing it;

(h) all monetary amounts are in Australian currency;

(i) a reference to time refers to Eastern Standard Time;

(j) includes is not a word of limitation; no rule of construction applies to the disadvantage of a party because these Terms are prepared by (or on behalf of) that party;

(k) a reference to any thing is a reference to the whole and each part of it;

(l) a reference to a group of persons is a reference to all of them collectively and to each of them individually; and

(m) a reference to a document includes all amendments or supplements to, or replacements or novations of, that document.

### 2. TERMS AND CONDITIONS

#### 2.1. Access to and use of this Website is governed by these Terms.

#### 2.2. West Maid periodically reviews the Terms and reserves the right to change the Terms, without any notice to you, by updating this document. You should review this document, as available on the Website, regularly as any changes to the Terms take immediate effect from the date of the publication on this document. Your continued use of the Website after any such changes are made will be deemed to constitute your acceptance of those changes.

#### 2.3. You acknowledge that any hyperlinks or other redirection tools taking you to other operated by third parties that appear on the Website (Third Party Sites) are not controlled by West Maid and do not form part of the Website. You agree that you will not hold West Maid liable or in any way accountable for anything that occurs on any Third Party Site.

### 3. ACCEPTANCE

#### 3.1. In order to use this Website and make a Booking, you must first agree to the Terms.

#### 3.2. You accept the Terms by:

(A) creating a User Profile; and

(b) clicking to accept/agree to the Terms.

#### 3.3. Notwithstanding clause 3.2, you may not accept the Terms or access the Website if:

(a) you are not of legal age to form a binding contract with West Maid; or

(b) you are a person barred from entering into contracts under legislation,

In which case, you must immediately leave the Website.

#### 3.4. By accepting the Terms, you agree that this is clear and unequivocal proof that the Terms are not unconscionable, that there is no unfair bargaining power or position, that there is no duress, and that you have carefully read and understood the Terms.

#### 3.5. If you do not understand any part of the Terms you should seek independent legal advice.

### 4. USER PROFILE

#### 4.1. You will be required to register your personal information, including your name, address, phone number and payment details on the Website in order to make a Booking (User Profile).

#### 4.2. You will be issued with a username and password which are linked to your User Profile. The username and password are personal to you and are not transferable. You are responsible for all information posted on or transmitted via the Booking System by anyone using your username and password and any payments due for the Cleaning Services acquired through the Booking System by anyone using your username and password. You should notify us of any breach of security of your username and password immediately.

#### 4.3. You confirm that you are at least 18 years of age and possess the legal authority to use the Booking System in accordance with these Terms. You also agree that all information supplied by you in using the Website and the Booking System will be true and accurate at all times.

#### 4.4. West Maid may delete or block User Profiles at its own discretion. Blocked users are prohibited from setting up a new User Profile.

### 5. BOOKING SYSTEM

#### 5.1. To make a Booking you must login to your User Profile and use the Booking System to request

a Booking. There is a minimum two (2) hour duration for hourly bookings and a minimum of one bedroom for flat priced bookings. You will receive a Booking confirmation receipt from West Maid after submitting your Booking request.

#### 5.2. West Maid will then make your contact details, location, requested time and the scope of the Cleaning Service available to their Cleaner network. An available Cleaner will then confirm their acceptance of the Booking.

#### 5.3. You are able to request a preferred Cleaner. West Maid will take your preference into account when facilitating the Cleaning Service, however a specific Cleaner cannot be guaranteed and will depend on the Cleaners availability.

#### 5.4. When a Booking is confirmed by a Cleaner, West Maid will issue you with an acceptance email and attach the Cleaning Agreement that constitutes the relationship between you and the Cleaner for the provision of the Cleaning services. West Maid will not, in anyway, be involved in the Cleaning Agreement between you and the Cleaner, aside from processing the Payment Amount on behalf of the Cleaner and providing you with an invoice in accordance with clause 6.4.

#### 5.5. If the requested Cleaner cannot fulfill your Booking, West Maid will arrange an alternative Cleaner for the requested Booking time.

#### 5.6. If the requested Booking cannot be facilitated, West Maid will arrange an alternative time for the Cleaning Service with you and a Cleaner.

#### 5.7. You are not permitted to engage the Cleaning Services of a Cleaner other than through the Booking System on the Website.

#### 5.8. The Booking System is provided on the Website to enable you to make legitimate Bookings and to make payments for those Bookings, and for no other purposes.

#### 5.9. Any speculative, false or fraudulent Booking is prohibited. You agree that the Booking System will only be used to make legitimate Bookings for you or another person for whom you are legally authorised to act. You acknowledge that abuse of the Booking System may result in you being denied access to the Booking System.

#### 5.10. West Maid has the right at any time to add, change or withdraw functions available on the Website at its own discretion.

### 6. PAYMENT

#### 6.1. You agree that at the time of the first Booking, your payment details will be transferred to West Maids secure payment gateway. Upon the successful Booking, West Maid will take payment for the Booking. You must ensure that sufficient funds are available for debit at that time. Fees and charges relating to insufficient funds at time of debit will be passed onto you.

#### 6.2. If you making a recurring Booking, your payment details will be transferred to West Maids secure payment gateway 48 hours prior to the scheduled Cleaning Services in the recurring booking, West Maid will take payment for the Cleaning Services. You must ensure that sufficient funds are available for debit at that time. Fees and charges relating to insufficient funds at time of debit will be passed onto you.

#### 6.3. On receipt of the Cleaning Fee, West Maid will hold the Cleaning Fee on behalf of the Cleaner until such time as it accounts to the Cleaner, pays a refund to you (if you are entitled to a refund) or credits payment of our fees and charges. No interest will be payable by West Maid to you or the Cleaner on amounts held by West Maid.

#### 6.4. West Maid, on behalf and in the name of the Cleaner, will issue you with a tax invoice.

#### 6.5. Late Payments, If for any reason your payment does not go through by 7 days of the service being completed, you will be sent a PayPal invoice to be paid within 10 days, If you dont pay the account with 10 days you agree to pay a late fee of $20 per day. If your account is still not paid after 14 days, it will be sent to collections. By using the services of West Maid, you agree to pay a compounded late fee as well as any fees associated with collection of the debt.

### 7. CHANGES AND CANCELLATIONS

#### 7.1. You can cancel or amend a Booking free of charge, up to 24 hours before the Cleaning Service is scheduled to begin.

#### 7.2. If you cancel or amend a Booking within 24 hours before the Cleaning Service is scheduled to begin, you will have to pay cancellation costs equivalent to one hour of the Cleaning Fee.

#### 7.3. You cannot amend, extend or cancel a Booking during the performance of the Services.

#### 7.4. The Cleaning Agreement shall expire once the Cleaning Services under the Booking have been performed.

#### 7.5. If the Cleaner is unable to fulfill a confirmed Booking (in full or part), West Maid will attempt to find you a replacement Cleaner. If we cannot find you an alternative Cleaner, we will reschedule your Booking to a new time which suits you. If we cannot find a suitable time for you, you may cancel the Booking at no charge.

### 8. CLEANING SERVICES

document.title: Top Benefits of Using a Residential Cleaning Company
document.description: Feeling overwhelmed by cleaning? Discover the life-changing benefits of hiring a residential cleaning company! Reclaim weekends, achieve a deep clean, reduce stress, and invest in your well-being. Breathe easy and live brighter with a spotless home!
document.author: kaung

body.raw:
Life in the modern world is hectic. Between juggling work, family, and social commitments, finding time to thoroughly clean your home can feel like an impossible feat. But here's the good news: you don't have to go it alone!  Hiring a residential cleaning company offers a multitude of benefits that can significantly improve your life.

**Gift Yourself the Gift of Time:**

Free up your weekends! Imagine waking up on a Saturday with a sparkling clean home, ready for relaxation or fun adventures. Professional cleaners can handle the cleaning, giving you more precious time to do the things you love.

**A Deep Clean You Can Trust:**

Say goodbye to surface-level cleaning! Professional cleaners are trained to tackle even the toughest jobs, reaching hidden corners and removing stubborn grime. This ensures a truly deep clean that leaves your home hygienically fresh.

**Reduced Stress and Improved Well-being:**

A clean home is a happy home! Coming home to a spotless environment can significantly reduce stress levels and contribute to a more positive outlook. Imagine the relief of knowing your cleaning worries are taken care of.

**Perfect for Busy Individuals and Families:**

Whether you're a busy professional or a family on the go, a residential cleaning company can be a lifesaver. Free up valuable time to focus on work, family activities, or pursuing your passions.

**More Than Just the Basics:**

Many cleaning companies offer a range of customizable services. Delegate carpet cleaning, oven degreasing, or even laundry folding for a truly comprehensive clean tailored to your specific needs.

**Professional Expertise at Your Fingertips:**

Professional cleaners use high-quality cleaning products and equipment. This ensures a more effective clean and reduces the risk of damaging your delicate furnishings.

**Invest in Your Home, Invest in Yourself:**

A clean home is an investment in your well-being. Reduced stress, a healthier environment for your family, and more free time - these are all valuable benefits that contribute to a higher quality of life.

**Finding Your Perfect Cleaning Match:**

The good news is, there's a residential cleaning company out there to suit your needs and budget. Research local companies and read reviews to find one that aligns with your preferences.

**Embrace a Brighter Life with a Clean Home**

Hiring a [residential cleaning company](https://westmaid.com.au) is more than just a luxury; it's an investment in your well-being and free time.  By delegating cleaning tasks, you can reclaim precious hours, reduce stress, and create a healthier, happier home environment.  Contact a reputable cleaning company today and take a step towards a brighter, more enjoyable life!

document.title: Why Professional Office Cleaning Services Matter In Perth
document.description: Unleash Perth's office shine! Discover how professional cleaning services boost employee health, productivity, and your brand image. Reduce sick days, elevate morale, and impress clients with a sparkling workspace.  Invest in a clean and thriving Perth business today!
document.author: kaung

body.raw:
Perth, a vibrant city known for its stunning beaches and booming business scene, thrives on a clean and professional image. For offices, maintaining a sparkling environment goes beyond aesthetics - it impacts employee well-being, productivity, and even your brand reputation.  Here's why investing in professional office cleaning services in Perth is a strategic decision.

**Health and Safety at the Forefront:**

A clean office is a healthy office. Professional cleaners use effective methods to remove dust, allergens, and germs, reducing the risk of illness among employees. This fosters a healthier work environment, leading to fewer sick days and a more productive workforce.

**A Spark for Employee Morale:**

First impressions matter, and a clean office creates a positive one. Employees working in a tidy and well-maintained space feel more valued and take greater pride in their surroundings. This can lead to improved morale, enhanced cooperation, and a more positive work environment.
Boosting Productivity and Efficiency:

Clutter breeds chaos! A clean and organized office allows employees to focus on their work without distractions. Professional cleaners ensure surfaces are clear, floors are spotless, and waste is properly disposed of, creating a streamlined workspace that fosters efficiency.

**Making a Powerful Impression:**

Client meetings and business gatherings are vital for Perth businesses. A clean and well-maintained office conveys professionalism and attention to detail, leaving a positive lasting impression on clients and potential partners. This can translate into increased business opportunities and a stronger brand image.

**Beyond the Basics: Expertise You Can Trust:**

Professional office cleaning services go beyond sweeping and mopping. Trained cleaners use specialized equipment and techniques to tackle tough jobs like carpet cleaning, window washing, and disinfecting high-touch surfaces. This ensures a comprehensive clean that reaches even the most neglected areas.

**Tailored Cleaning Solutions for Perth Businesses:**

No two offices are the same. Professional cleaning companies offer customized plans to suit your specific needs and budget. Whether you require daily cleaning, weekly deep cleans, or specialized services, there's a solution to fit your requirements.

**Free Up Your Time and Resources:**

Focus on your core business! By delegating cleaning tasks to professionals, you free up valuable in-house resources to focus on core business activities. This allows your team to concentrate on what they do best, maximizing productivity and achieving business goals.

**Investing in a Clean and Healthy Work Environment:**

Professional office cleaning services are an investment in your business. The benefits go beyond aesthetics, leading to a healthier workforce, improved productivity, and a stronger brand image. For Perth businesses, a clean office is a shining advantage in today's competitive landscape.

**Finding Your Perfect Cleaning Match:**

Perth boasts a diverse range of professional cleaning companies. Research local firms, compare services, and choose a company that aligns with your budget and specific needs.

**Embrace a Clean and Productive Perth Workplace**

Investing in [professional office cleaning services in Perth](https://westmaid.com.au/office-cleaning-perth) is a strategic decision.  By prioritizing a clean and healthy work environment, you're not just creating a positive space for your employees - you're investing in the success of your business.  Contact a reputable cleaning company today and experience the Perth shine!
